Class HapiConverter<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cerner.bunsen.definitions.HapiConverter<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    HapiChoiceConverter, HapiCompositeConverter, HapiContainedConverter, LeafExtensionConverter, NoOpConverter, PrimitiveConverter

    public abstract class HapiConverter<T>
extends Object
    Base class for converting HAPI resources to an alternative object model, such as Spark rows or Avro objects.
